sters, but heating through dynamical friction could expand the cluster\nto a similar extent. The examined clusters expand well within their tidal radii\nand would survive gas expulsion even in a strong tidal field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2016 21:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2016 14:37:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-29"}
