lower velocities. We\nalso present calculations for the He I 10830 \\AA~and 2 $\\mu$m lines for a lower\nmass (low luminosity) double detonation model, which has a post-explosion He\nmass of 0.077 $M_{\\odot}$. In this case, both the He I features we consider are\nstrong and can provide a clear observational signature of the double-detonation\nmechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2016 01:10:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-01"}
