ting mass-loss with an\nefficiency of 40% or the donor star is undergoing quasi-cyclic variations due\nto a varying mass-quadrupole induced by either a strong (1 kG) field or by some\nunidentified mechanism probably linked to irradiation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2016 09:54:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-14"}
