ansfer of\nphoton's energy to electronic system and large $\\tau_{th}$. We also predict\nthat even several microns wide dirty superconducting bridge is able to detect\nsingle near-infrared or optical photon if its critical current exceeds 70 $\\%$\nof depairing current and $C_e/C_{ph}|_{T_c} \\gtrsim 1$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2016 12:33:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Dec 2016 10:51:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2017 06:06:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-29"}
